snippet.title: Compartmentalize Any% 13:40
snippet.description: A narrative Sokoban puzzler about grief, anger, reflection, and other complex emotions and feelings created for the Lady Arcaders Game Jam (LAG Jam 2024). "Sokoban" refers to the mechanic of moving objects around a level towards a marked goal.
